snippet.title: Our Kickstarter is live! Support Paradox - Paradox - a Cube Escape game & Rusty Lake Short Film
snippet.description:
We hope you guys can support our new project Paradox - a Cube Escape game & Rusty Lake Short Film on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1668831552/paradox-a-cube-escape-game-and-rusty-lake-short-fi

This is the first time you can really become part of a Rusty Lake project and we have done our best to create a cool selection of rewards, full of Rusty Lake merchandising, props from the movie and more.

Feel free to some questions about the project or kickstarter, maybe you guys have some feedback just let me know!

Thanks for the support!
